00:00:12.416 --> 00:00:15.008
(I'm the queen of Hard-Labor Ward.)

00:00:15.008 --> 00:00:17.856
(Hard-Labor Ward)

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:21.000
We need to hurry up.

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:25.240
Once I save enough money,

00:00:25.344 --> 00:00:26.720
I'll surely bribe Madam Li

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:29.480
to get assigned to deliver meals
to the Cold Palace.

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:30.680
It's easy work

00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:31.920
with extra to skim.

00:00:32.160 --> 00:00:33.960
No more washing stinky clothes
every day.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:36.280
Who wouldn't want that?

00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:38.880
Everyone knows Cold Palace
meal delivery is the easiest.

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:41.280
People lining up to bribe Madam Li

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:42.440
fight tooth and nail.

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:46.600
Those cushy jobs

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:48.840
are getting more expensive.

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:54.120
Ladies,

00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:57.120
that Cold Palace delivery job
is so good.

00:00:57.360 --> 00:00:57.960
Lately,

00:00:57.960 --> 00:00:59.000
who's been doing it?

00:01:00.360 --> 00:01:00.960
Go away!

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:01.880
Get lost!

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:02.440
You reek!

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:03.680
You pot-scrubber,

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:05.880
dare ask about Cold Palace deliveries?

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:07.120
You're unworthy!

00:01:09.480 --> 00:01:11.000
You want the Cold Palace job too?

00:01:11.808 --> 00:01:13.080
(Rong Xiaolan)

00:01:13.080 --> 00:01:13.880
Got money?

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:15.960
I don't.

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:19.760
Then stop asking.

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:32.080
Silence!

00:01:32.080 --> 00:01:32.840
Back to work!

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:37.640
Lu Jiuning,

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:40.880
Lady Yu herself ordered me

00:01:40.960 --> 00:01:42.040
to give you

00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:43.480
special care.

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:45.240
Listen well.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:47.280
A hundred more nightsoil pots

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:48.360
are coming later.

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:49.760
If you don't scrub them all,

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:51.440
don't even think about eating.

00:01:53.520 --> 00:01:54.480
Go!

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:57.240
Go!

00:02:13.240 --> 00:02:13.960
Madam,

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:15.400
I'm saving up silver.

00:02:15.640 --> 00:02:17.160
I'll show my respect once it's enough.

00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:18.480
Please assign me

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:20.480
an easy job then.

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:21.720
Relax.

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:23.520
Madam Li,

00:02:23.640 --> 00:02:24.880
I'm saving up too.

00:02:25.088 --> 00:02:25.680
Good.

00:02:26.440 --> 00:02:28.160
Hard-Labor Ward slaves

00:02:28.320 --> 00:02:28.800
work

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:30.200
from mao hour

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:31.840
till hai hour.

00:02:32.320 --> 00:02:34.920
It's all the hardest, back-breaking work
day and night.

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:37.320
But as they say,

00:02:37.640 --> 00:02:38.480
with money,

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:39.880
you can make devils grind.

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.280
If you're tired,

00:02:41.840 --> 00:02:43.120
bring me silver

00:02:43.640 --> 00:02:44.280
to exchange

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:45.600
for lighter duties.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.200
If you think

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:49.200
saving is too slow,

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:50.080
why not

00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:52.200
borrow from my moneylender.

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:54.400
Just pay

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:56.200
the interest on time.

00:02:56.880 --> 00:02:57.360
We

00:02:57.520 --> 00:02:58.280
can always

00:02:58.280 --> 00:02:59.320
work something out.

00:03:00.440 --> 00:03:01.200
Yes, yes!

00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:01.800
Okay.

00:03:03.480 --> 00:03:04.560
It's really good.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:05.680
Let me continue.

00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:06.840
Good.

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.720
You're Jiuning?

00:03:41.600 --> 00:03:42.760
Your hands are raw, right?

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.840
I scrubbed pots before,

00:03:45.320 --> 00:03:47.920
hands bled daily.

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:51.440
This is dandelion paste.

00:03:51.600 --> 00:03:52.720
Put it on wounds.

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:53.680
It eases pain.

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:54.440
Try it.

00:03:59.080 --> 00:03:59.880
Thanks.

00:04:00.160 --> 00:04:00.880
Do you

00:04:00.880 --> 00:04:03.320
want the Cold Palace job too?

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.000
Forget it.

00:04:06.320 --> 00:04:08.880
Several tried bribing Madam Li recently.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:10.680
None succeeded.

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.000
These days,

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:13.600
she delivers meals herself.

00:04:15.712 --> 00:04:16.920
She did it herself?

00:04:17.840 --> 00:04:18.240
Yes.

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:19.960
Xiaolan,

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.296
when will you repay
the 80 taels of silver

00:04:23.296 --> 00:04:24.320
you owe Madam Li?

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:26.600
You haven't paid the interest
for two months.

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:27.880
I'll pay.

00:04:28.064 --> 00:04:29.160
Please, have mercy!

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:31.280
Hard-Labor Ward wages are too meager.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:32.960
Please give me a few more days.

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:33.880
So you mean

00:04:34.200 --> 00:04:35.680
you still don't have the money today?

00:04:36.480 --> 00:04:37.160
Xiaolan,

00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:39.712
why haven't you repaid
Madam Li's debt yet?

00:04:40.200 --> 00:04:41.040
You make the eunuchs

00:04:41.200 --> 00:04:43.240
come here for nothing.

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:44.840
Not just the eunuchs,

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:46.560
even I'm losing patience.

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:48.280
What bad luck.

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:49.440
Please.

00:04:49.640 --> 00:04:50.960
Give me a few more days,

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:52.080
okay?

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:54.880
More time?

00:04:55.200 --> 00:04:56.672
You've delayed for two months.

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:58.000
When you borrowed the money,

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:59.840
you signed an IOU in black and white.

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:01.160
If you don't pay up,

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:02.960
we won't be so polite.

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:06.080
If you keep delaying,

00:05:06.520 --> 00:05:09.000
we'll have to get serious with you.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:11.160
How about today

00:05:11.320 --> 00:05:12.520
you pay some interest first?

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:14.360
No money?

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:16.760
Then pay with your body.

00:05:17.200 --> 00:05:18.200
Entertain us

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:20.000
for some fun.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:20.560
Ah!

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:22.880
Let go!

00:05:22.880 --> 00:05:23.360
Come on!

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:23.960
Let go of me!

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:28.192
Let go of me!

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:32.560
Who?

00:05:33.200 --> 00:05:33.792
Who did this?

00:05:34.320 --> 00:05:35.120
You lowly maid!

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:36.320
Do you know who I work for?

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:37.200
You dare hit me?

00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:38.120
Yes, I hit you!

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:42.016
This may be the Hard-Labor Ward,

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.640
but it's still imperial harem.

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:44.680
Right in the palace,

00:05:44.680 --> 00:05:45.480
you defy the law

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.160
and disregard palace rules.

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:48.400
Debts must be repaid.

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:49.200
That's justice.

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:49.800
Debt?

00:05:50.280 --> 00:05:51.080
Whose debt?

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:52.440
Why the debt?

00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:54.320
Why 80 taels of silver?

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:56.920
Speak!

00:05:58.040 --> 00:05:58.880
Don't get cocky.

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:00.240
If you interfere,

00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:01.800
Madam Li won't spare you.

00:06:01.880 --> 00:06:02.720
Since childhood,

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:05.120
I've seen plenty of bullies
who rely on your master's power.

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:06.280
They fear you,

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:07.280
but I don't!

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:08.720
Show me

00:06:09.040 --> 00:06:09.760
what you've got!

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:11.520
Come on!

00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:13.200
Let's go.

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:14.000
Go.

00:06:18.640 --> 00:06:19.240
Are you okay?

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:22.680
Lu Jiuning,

00:06:23.200 --> 00:06:24.280
you always play the hero!

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:25.920
If Madam Li gets angry

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:26.840
and comes here,

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:28.440
we'll all suffer.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:29.360
Exactly!

00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:31.000
We're so unlucky.

00:06:31.400 --> 00:06:32.400
Who dares

00:06:32.400 --> 00:06:33.840
cross Madam Li?

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:35.440
Hear that?

00:06:36.120 --> 00:06:37.360
Sharing a room with you

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.840
is the worst misfortune!

00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:40.480
We live under the same roof.

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:42.120
Not only don't help when trouble comes,

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:43.600
but aid the abusers,

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:44.520
mocking others.

00:06:45.080 --> 00:06:48.128
You're just a coward.

00:06:50.520 --> 00:06:51.480
How dare you lecture me?

00:06:52.080 --> 00:06:53.024
In the Hard-Labor Ward,

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:54.640
Madam Li makes the rules.

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:56.520
Did any of those

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:58.440
who opposed her before end well?

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:02.760
Let go.

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:07.200
Madam Li acts so brazenly

00:07:07.200 --> 00:07:08.360
and bullies you freely

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:11.400
precisely because you're all selfish.

00:07:11.400 --> 00:07:12.400
You think of yourselves

00:07:12.520 --> 00:07:13.600
and won't stand together.

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:16.240
With so many in the Hard-Labor Ward,

00:07:17.080 --> 00:07:18.880
if we stood together

00:07:19.240 --> 00:07:20.320
and helped each other,

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:22.480
how could they act so viciously?

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:26.000
I'm just warning you.

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:29.680
If you stay this selfish,

00:07:30.280 --> 00:07:31.240
those who oppress you

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.960
will only grow crueler.

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:35.000
By then,

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.640
you'll be wiped out

00:07:36.840 --> 00:07:38.520
without a trace.

00:07:48.320 --> 00:07:49.280
Alright, enough.

00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:49.960
Go to sleep.

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:54.600
Xiaolan,

00:07:55.920 --> 00:07:57.040
how did you end up

00:07:57.160 --> 00:07:58.280
owing them so much money?

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:01.040
My mother was gravely ill.

00:08:01.320 --> 00:08:02.680
To pay for her treatment,

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:04.760
I borrowed money from Madam Li.

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:05.800
The interest was high.

00:08:06.200 --> 00:08:06.720
She even

00:08:09.200 --> 00:08:10.360
sketched me nude,

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.600
made me sign and seal it,

00:08:12.640 --> 00:08:14.000
and used my honor as collateral,

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:15.400
pledging my body to her.

00:08:17.400 --> 00:08:18.960
If I couldn't pay the interest,

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:22.080
she'd arrange to pair me with a eunuch.

00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:24.320
Or she might assign me

00:08:24.320 --> 00:08:25.040
to serve

00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:27.600
those powerful eunuchs or guards.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:33.240
Many of us who couldn't bear
the humiliation jumped into wells.

00:08:35.328 --> 00:08:38.208
I don't know how many more days
I can endure.

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:41.800
Madam Li

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:43.960
is truly deranged.

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:47.000
After all, we were born low

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:48.000
and meant to serve.

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:51.480
Madam Li dares commit
all these atrocities here

00:08:52.040 --> 00:08:53.920
because Lady Yu backs her.

00:08:55.280 --> 00:08:56.520
We servants

00:08:57.040 --> 00:08:58.080
can only accept our fate.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:00.880
Retribution will come.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.160
It's just not time yet.

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:07.400
They deserve to die.

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:11.232
(Hard-Labor Ward)

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.760
Look at this embroidery.

00:09:33.080 --> 00:09:34.200
And this fabric.

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:35.640
This

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.920
is what proper masters should wear.

00:09:38.680 --> 00:09:39.920
If they can wear it,

00:09:39.920 --> 00:09:40.240
hmph,

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:42.000
so can I.

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.392
Madam Li.

00:09:52.400 --> 00:09:53.440
I am here.

00:09:55.400 --> 00:09:56.560
You may leave.

00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.160
Yes, Your Highness.

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:07.800
I grovel before the masters daily,

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:09.320
flattering and fawning.

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:12.560
But here in Hard-Labor Ward,

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:15.840
I am the supreme ruler.

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:19.560
I am

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:21.600
the Empress of Hard-Labor Ward!

00:10:29.400 --> 00:10:30.600
(Madam Li,)

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:32.880
(I was just wondering
how to make you talk,)

00:10:33.800 --> 00:10:35.720
(and you came to me yourself.)

00:10:41.640 --> 00:10:42.440
Lu Jiuning,

00:10:42.840 --> 00:10:44.400
can't you work faster?

00:10:45.680 --> 00:10:46.880
Hurry up,

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:47.800
Lu Jiuning!

00:10:47.826 --> 00:10:49.400
(Hard-Labor Ward)

00:10:49.400 --> 00:10:50.240
It stinks.

00:10:50.520 --> 00:10:51.840
I'm so unlucky

00:10:52.200 --> 00:10:53.120
to be paired with you.

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:55.680
We always get these filthy tasks!

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:13.000
Lord Ning,

00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:14.160
don't go that way.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:15.200
By regulations,

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:17.040
royal family members mustn't wander

00:11:17.040 --> 00:11:18.000
through the inner court.

00:11:18.400 --> 00:11:19.640
You think I don't know rules?

00:11:20.200 --> 00:11:20.920
Then you...

00:11:24.400 --> 00:11:25.480
It's her again.

00:11:27.648 --> 00:11:30.272
(Hard-Labor Ward)

00:11:36.440 --> 00:11:37.400
Greetings, Lord Ning.

00:11:48.160 --> 00:11:49.040
You're

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:50.120
the firefly girl

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:51.360
who caught His Majesty's eye?

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:55.800
Your memory serves you well.

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:57.080
I'm Lu Jiuning.

00:11:57.800 --> 00:11:58.760
Lady Wan has passed.

00:12:00.840 --> 00:12:01.600
My condolences.

00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:05.360
What surprises me is

00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:07.320
how someone as clever as you

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.240
could make such a mistake

00:12:10.040 --> 00:12:11.880
to slander and attack imperial consorts,

00:12:12.040 --> 00:12:13.480
ending up in Hard-Labor Ward?

00:12:14.160 --> 00:12:15.800
You shouldn't ask about harem affairs.

00:12:18.360 --> 00:12:19.320
You maid

00:12:20.080 --> 00:12:21.120
have quite the temper.

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:23.800
But in the imperial harem,

00:12:24.480 --> 00:12:25.480
temper alone

00:12:26.560 --> 00:12:27.760
will get you into trouble.

00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:30.800
Without power or connections,

00:12:31.280 --> 00:12:32.800
you dare to anger noble ladies.

00:12:33.520 --> 00:12:35.120
If you keep acting recklessly,

00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:37.000
you'll lose your head.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:43.320
Are you done lecturing me?

00:12:43.840 --> 00:12:45.040
I have work to do.

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:46.440
I beg to take my leave.

00:12:47.520 --> 00:12:48.120
Lu Jiuning,

00:12:48.520 --> 00:12:49.840
His Highness is showing concern!

00:12:49.840 --> 00:12:51.000
What's that attitude?

00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:54.400
Your Highness,

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:55.880
if you truly care,

00:12:56.040 --> 00:12:57.360
you should talk to His Majesty

00:12:57.920 --> 00:12:59.040
and ask him

00:12:59.040 --> 00:13:00.520
to clear Wan'er's name.

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:02.000
Imperial harem affairs

00:13:02.360 --> 00:13:03.200
are tangled.

00:13:04.400 --> 00:13:05.280
I can't step in.

00:13:06.600 --> 00:13:07.480
So,

00:13:08.360 --> 00:13:09.560
servants remain servants.

00:13:09.720 --> 00:13:10.920
The lowborn stay lowborn.

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.160
Nobles

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:14.040
are lofty masters above us.

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:15.560
How could we dare to offend them?

00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:18.200
Even when we suffer
wrongful accusations,

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:19.440
ultimately

00:13:20.400 --> 00:13:22.040
we have to swallow our grievances

00:13:22.520 --> 00:13:23.280
to keep the peace.

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:25.960
Jiuning.

00:13:27.920 --> 00:13:28.560
I know

00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:30.240
behind your current plight

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:32.520
or your schemes

00:13:33.440 --> 00:13:34.120
lies some

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:36.720
grander design.

00:13:38.400 --> 00:13:39.400
I'm just warning you.

00:13:40.320 --> 00:13:41.680
Proceed with utmost caution.

00:13:42.120 --> 00:13:42.912
Don't act rashly.

00:13:43.160 --> 00:13:44.200
In this imperial harem

00:13:44.920 --> 00:13:46.440
never underestimate anyone.

00:13:56.032 --> 00:13:57.728
(Hard-Labor Ward)

00:14:02.120 --> 00:14:02.800
(Your Highness,)

00:14:03.560 --> 00:14:04.880
(I have no other choice.)

00:14:05.560 --> 00:14:06.760
(If I falter,)

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:09.280
(who will clear Wan'er's name?)

00:14:10.760 --> 00:14:11.680
(You think)

00:14:12.040 --> 00:14:13.360
(I'm powerless)

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:15.720
(and see my demand
for justice for Wan'er)

00:14:16.120 --> 00:14:17.280
(as mere recklessness,)

00:14:18.640 --> 00:14:20.320
(but I'll show you all)

00:14:20.840 --> 00:14:22.160
(even an ant has its dignity)

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:23.760
(and mayflies can shake trees.)

00:14:25.440 --> 00:14:27.560
(Madam Li rules Hard-Labor Ward,)

00:14:27.800 --> 00:14:28.880
(abusing palace servants.)

00:14:30.440 --> 00:14:32.160
(I'll tear her down first)

00:14:33.320 --> 00:14:34.840
(and take her place.)